'''哈扎拉吉語'''（{{lang-fa|هزارگی یا آزرگی}}）屬於[[印歐語系|印歐語系]][[印度-伊朗語族|印度-伊朗語族]]，是一種在[[阿富汗|阿富汗]]、[[伊朗|伊朗]]、[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]和[[塔吉克斯坦|塔吉克斯坦]]等[[國家|國家]]由[[蒙古人|蒙古人]][[血統|血統]]的[[哈扎拉族|哈扎拉族]]使用的[[語言|語言]] <ref>[[Franz_Schurmann|Schurmann, Franz]] (1962) ''The Mongols of Afghanistan: An Ethnography of the Moghôls and Related Peoples of Afghanistan'' Mouton, The Hague, Netherlands, - page 17, [http://worldcat.org/oclc/401634 OCLC 401634] {{Wayback|url=http://worldcat.org/oclc/401634 |date=20081206023436 }}</ref>。哈扎拉吉語借用了許多[[突厥語族|突厥語族]]與[[蒙古語族|蒙古語族]]詞彙。

== 分類 ==
哈扎拉吉語被學者列為單獨語言<ref>Malistani, A. H. Tariq and Gehring, Roman (compilers) (1993) ''Farhang-i ibtidal-i milli-i Hazarah : bi-inzimam-i tarjamah bih Farsi-i Ingilisi = Hazaragi - Dari/Persian - English: a preliminary glossary'' A. H. Tariq Malistani, Quetta, [http://worldcat.org/oclc/33814814 OCLC 33814814] {{Wayback|url=http://worldcat.org/oclc/33814814 |date=20080612103758 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ethnologue.com/show_language.asp?code=haz |title="Ethnologue Report on Hazaragi" |accessdate=2009-06-27 |archive-date=2009-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307094247/http://www.ethnologue.com/show_language.asp?code=haz |dead-url=no }}</ref> 和波斯語的方言之一 <ref>Dulling, G. K. (1973) ''The Hazaragi dialect of Afghan Persian'' Central Asian Research Centre, London, [http://worldcat.org/oclc/703532 OCLC 703532]</ref>. 它很容易與其他[[阿富汗|阿富汗]][[波斯|波斯]]方言分別出來 <ref>[[Franz_Schurmann|Schurmann, Franz]] (1962) ''The Mongols of Afghanistan: An Ethnography of the Moghôls and Related Peoples of Afghanistan'' Mouton, The Hague, Netherlands, - page 110, [http://worldcat.org/oclc/401634 OCLC 401634] {{Wayback|url=http://worldcat.org/oclc/401634 |date=20081206023436 }}</ref>。 哈扎拉吉語包含不少[[蒙古語族|蒙古語族]]及[[突厥語族|突厥]]詞彙.

